products.productName: Pichu & Pikachu Pokémon Sweet Support Plush - 7 In.
products.description: During tough times, long days, or just moments when you need extra comfort, it's important to find time for a big hug—whether it's with friends, loved ones, pets, or Pokémon plush. This Pokémon Sweet Support plush features Pikachu consoling Pichu, as the latter lets out a good cry. The two are connected via a cord, so when you pull them apart, Pichu runs back into Pikachu's arms. Send this pair to someone who needs a little boost of support.

products.description: When the weather outside is frightful, Pokémon celebrate the holidays under the sea!
